{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhwt4pnymqg0","created":1776568943556,"text":"助人行为"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhwuege7n3k0","created":1776572528127,"text":" 社会行为的起源"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhwynlgx7qg0","created":1776584528892,"text":"基因的遗传造成了行为的先天性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhwynp9tsrc0","created":1776584537170,"text":"社会生物学视角"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhwynxh4yq80","created":1776584555026,"text":"人与人之间的相互作用\n以最大化利益/最小化代价为目的"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhwyok29ck00","created":1776584604193,"text":"社会交换理论"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhwyov8dobk0","created":1776584628507,"text":"社会规范的随处可见本身\n构成了学习规范的文化基础"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhwypph61xc0","created":1776584694342,"text":"社会规范论"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhwyqiznsb40","created":1776584758587,"text":"某种行动能够带来收益\n产生这种行为的心理机制就能得到强化"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhwyqwf6f1s0","created":1776584787823,"text":"进化心理学视角"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhwytfrag5k0","created":1776584986643,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}